{"tid":1503142,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"幫 警員親屬連線 除口罩大行動","createTime":"2019-08-24T23:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T23:57:57.000Z","uid":282910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2b14f32190e68f0bc808bbbebc376ec85fe5a2","tid":1503142,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T23:57:57.000Z","msg":"今日就係<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【警員親屬連線集會-還警於民】大集會！</div><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PoliceRelativesConnection/posts/118728936127197?__tn__=K-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPoliceRelativesConnection%2Fposts%2F118728936127197%3F__tn__%3DK-R&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUKVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=b507330c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PoliceRelativesConnection/posts/118728936127197?__tn__=K-R</a><br />\n<br />\n原來佢地因為怕俾人起底，所以鼓勵所有參加面蒙面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂阿哥，咁黑警都去得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係黑警都參加扮白警啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n市民就會覺得﹕「原來重有咁多白警！我對警隊重捨希望了！」<br />\n<br />\n所以我係度發起「鼓勵」佢地除口罩大行動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 白警頂天立地有咩好怕？<br />\n勇武都俾泛民叫除口罩，聽日唔好一個泛民叫佢地除口罩都無啊。<br />\n<br />\nps 千祈唔好混入去扯佢地口罩啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}